[Comerciante gato tembloroso]

jukfBA.en: - A white cat. You looked at her carefully and found a partially black stain. -
jukfBA.es: -Una gata blanca. La miras con cuidado y le notas una mancha parcialmente negra.-

j+kfBA.en: - You got close to her and she blocks your path. Maybe she is trying to protect the pile of sand. Investigate it. -
j+kfBA.es: -Te acercaste y te bloquea el paso. Quizás intenta proteger la pila de arena. Investígalo.-

kukfBA.en: - You investigated the Pile_of_sand and found ^FF0000white bones^000000 that seem to belong to a small animal. -
kukfBA.es: -Investigaste la pila de arena y encontraste ^660000huesos blancos^000000 que parecen pertenecerle a un animal pequeño.-

k+kfBA.en:
- Among the bones, there is a worn out ^FF0000Red Packing_Ribbon ^000000. 
It seems to be the lead of a small animal. -
k+kfBA.es:
-Entre los huesos, hay un ^660000moño rojo de embalar desgastado ^000000. 
Parece ser la correa de un animal pequeño.-

lOkfBA.en:
- Maybe you found her too late...
Now, collect the bones and go back to Jakk. -
lOkfBA.es:
-Quizás la encontraste demasiado tarde…
Ahora, recoge los huesos y regresa con Jakk.-
